              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/124238/stephan-muller&quot; title=&quot;25,968 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Stephan Muller&lt;/a&gt;
