                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;I think the signal to noise ratio in this answer is way too low. It&apos;s supposed to be about Scanner, but there&apos;s things like immutability, sets vs switch, and a lot of other things. When you go around marking questions that can be answered in 3 lines of code as a duplicate of this you do nothing more but confuse them. Contrasted with the NRE canonical, NREs require that depth. Scanner doesn&apos;t.&lt;/span&gt;

