            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Despite the other answers listed above, this one turned out to be the correct one for me.  I initially got the &quot;cannot find APK&quot; message when I went to compile some sample code, then did a Clean which generated a ton of &quot;R cannot be resolved&quot; errors, and then just opening the .xml file and manually saving it the errors were cleared and I could compile.&lt;/span&gt;

