            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;+1 for this was my issue. You must name your images like so: eicon.png not eIcon.png. I found the error by looking at the Consol. It was returning an error on the file with Invalid File Name:...&lt;/span&gt;

